  "text": "Thank you. I don't wish to cover ground that we've covered before, but it sometimes is helpful to restate these concepts for complete clarity since words are a poor tool for what we do. Just as a passing point, I was wondering on this planet during the second density, I believed there was habitation at the same time space of bipedal entities and what we call the dinosaurs. Is this correct? I am raw. This is correct.",
